{"tid":290454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【專家警告】謝國忠：能賣掉趕快賣！港樓泡沫或迎廿年大蕭條!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-06-19T18:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T01:32:08.000Z","uid":22675,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb4918587941ee868e288f5e852779065b59b79","tid":290454,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T18:57:32.000Z","msg":"2017年06月19日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170619/large/1497868553_ed18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170619%2Flarge%2F1497868553_ed18.jpg&h=8e5b5f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾預測97年亞洲金融風暴的經濟學家謝國忠今日接受電視台訪問時警告，香港樓市已出現泡沫，更可以隨時爆破，未來更迎接長達20年的樓市大蕭條。<br />\n謝國忠認為，本港樓市已「風高浪急」：「樓市向下行的走勢不像97年、98年那麼簡單，因為當年有危機，外資都撤出香港。現在利息一下就會上升，有些人認為樓市還會上升，我覺得非常不理性。」<br />\n謝國忠又警告：「如果你全部投資都放在房地產上，我勸你能賣的趕快賣掉，這是最後一次機會。」他認為香樓市已出現泡沫，爆破後或迎接長達20年的樓市大蕭條。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170619/56848954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170619%2F56848954&d=Gxbg3acvTSw8hrhjSEijCf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d3393191\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170619%2F56848954&h=8b97c636\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170619/56848954</a>"},{"pid":"14e76b3db4aa15acef4d7fe5e154db3cad94653c","tid":290454,"uid":48582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T19:02:06.000Z","msg":"佢預測樓市唔太準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係聽住先會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e6a47111a354c41a3a488671fb8ebd1562fdd9","tid":290454,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T19:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢預測樓市唔太準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm