近期破裂&rdquo;一文，開啟了近十年的&ldquo;唱空中國樓市之旅&rdquo;。&ldquo;十年如一日&rdquo;地堅持認為中國房地產存在&ldquo;嚴重泡沫&ldquo;，並於近兩年不斷給出房價跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n但是，記者查閱公開資料發現，謝國忠近十年間的20餘次&ldquo;涉房&rdquo;言論鮮有應驗。官方公佈的統計數據總是見漲，讓他的言論在現實面前不堪一擊。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;2012年中國樓市終將破滅&rdquo;，這是謝國忠在2009年年的預測。及至2010年，他先後8次表示&ldquo;中國房地產已進入熊市，未來五年大城市房價跌一半&rdquo;，其中他稱&ldquo;樓市泡沫破滅時，我會通知大家&ldquo;。<br />\n<br />\n謝國忠在2011年給出房價具體下跌幅度，&ldquo;房價跌幅很快達到25％，未來兩到三年會繼續同樣跌幅。&rdquo;同時，他預測2012年是中國房地產的拐點。謝國忠在2012年曾先後預測中國房價&ldquo;會在未來5年內跌50％&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n事實卻是，2009年年以來的中國樓市幾乎不間斷地持續瘋長。國家統計局公佈的數據顯示，2009年年全年70大中城市房價上漲1.5％。2010年的房價漲勢更迅猛，全年月均最高值為12.8％，最低值為6.4％。2011年略微下降，2012年再次反彈。<br />\n<br />\n近日(2013)，一則&ldquo;謝國忠：中國房地產泡沫未來數月內破滅，最多不到一年&rdquo;的消息大鬧地產界，同時，也將這位&ldquo;屢敗屢戰&rdquo;的預言家再一次推上風口浪尖。<br />\n<br />\n信哩條友講樓市真係你諗你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢次次都話冧市,肯定會比佢up中一次</blockquote><br />\n唔信，一次都唔會中<br />\n香港樓市只會不斷向上，唔會跌</blockquote><br />\n中咗一次咪拎住中嗰次係咁吹自己準囉<br />\n專家就係咁出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢其實中左，但係大陸有 n 樣花招唔比個市跌，結果佢同朗咸平一齊做左支爆孖寶比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efa509b803931f51ad1150f064cd6a098c2f386","tid":290454,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"睇吓中國撐得幾耐？"},{"pid":"09b9f8d355c392874fd64c9a1188028df0c0e32a","tid":290454,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇吓中國撐得幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n撐埋呢一次，之後美帝抽走資金就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b7f015e3c265b5f1cd33ab0878c353c7170dd3","tid":290454,"uid":99973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"爆係遲早既事<br />\n但幾時要問水晶球了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba88ca9f31d7e4ecb5f3e9785129f618bf06030","tid":290454,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"林太"},{"pid":"9c521c95adb0cb62ba9931f8c47ac41ea94ce862","tid":290454,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4050b6c4acc614b30a77796e9668a3f728f0f4a","tid":290454,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"一日有支那黨都唔會跌wo大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n400呎800萬不是夢先係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1616c8fe68e53021d63768a35c20c71a2ed55f01","tid":290454,"uid":25307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"賣左我訓街？"},{"pid":"b44d9fb28b9ec815c02a2f2d6f30bbfc5c596720","tid":290454,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:32:57.000Z","msg":"講在幾耐<br />\n唔爭在講到爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6997b59cf46ca6e1e8af6a44e3ad7eac367e4931","tid":290454,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"一爆啲支那人會唔會狂買？"},{"pid":"ed5cd0db8b5f7e8a98bf4807f100a47c8a6c813f","tid":290454,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"跌一半都重有一半，之後又升返。"},{"pid":"48610dc67ed4ba30cdc45b7b9c1948810a789cb3","tid":290454,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1c7a9dc020afaf49711a3cc5d886cf09918ee0","tid":290454,"uid":35716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"睇唔到有乜原因大陸人會賣走港樓....."},{"pid":"422b6dd8658c02b962e39d5177cb470ffd276e62","tid":290454,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇唔到有乜原因大陸人會賣走港樓.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人民幣定期利息一年由2.8升到4.3, 香港收租連2厘都無.........."},{"pid":"40051df79f670a2521d52ef557c669ea39467bed","tid":290454,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇唔到有乜原因大陸人會賣走港樓.....</blockquote><br />\n賣香港樓，買外國樓"},{"pid":"329d7d0114ea404eb65867e0948c8f6a75d54cff","tid":290454,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b173596ca65de36e9be454ea9d0ea30d563814a","tid":290454,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:03:37.000Z","msg":"燈夠未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc5aeccdd6121a86400c8e69c8fc3ba981ec2c7","tid":290454,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:04:09.000Z","msg":"樓市會轉淡，甚至會跌，完全唔出奇&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n話樓市會爆破，亦都唔係無可能&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但係以依家嘅銀行體系，話樓市爆到香港經濟蕭條，不如話支爆導致全球經濟蕭條，從而影響香港&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n以現時經濟週期越縮越短（因為資信流通太快），無乜理由會經濟蕭條二十年噃&hellip;＂二十年＂係點計出嚟嘅呢？"},{"pid":"2c6b0ead0a0000cfb80e236f455711b8fe1fec5b","tid":290454,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:11:21.000Z","msg":"呢條友都唱淡左好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca2d9706b9907d1fe7dabddf6863ea60e4d0a0a","tid":290454,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:31:37.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾都有人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd9dd552d1128ade3dd43bb1193b74ea24f17dd","tid":290454,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"食屎啦你"},{"pid":"0ce347df850ccaeb9bd7806ae470d12a4a6c1814","tid":290454,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓市會轉淡，甚至會跌，完全唔出奇&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n話樓市會爆破，亦都唔係無可能&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但係以依家嘅銀行體系，話樓市爆到香港經濟蕭條，不如話支爆導致全球經濟蕭條，從而影響香港&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n以現時經濟週期越縮越短（因為資信流通太快），無乜理由會經濟蕭條二十年噃&hellip;＂二十年＂係點計出嚟嘅呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本樓市跌左30年wow."},{"pid":"ee91bc10bb96d3cdc5276a0026fdde6a4e9cb05c","tid":290454,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓市會轉淡，甚至會跌，完全唔出奇&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n話樓市會爆破，亦都唔係無可能&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但係以依家嘅銀行體系，話樓市爆到香港經濟蕭條，不如話支爆導致全球經濟蕭條，從而影響香港&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n以現時經濟週期越縮越短（因為資信流通太快），無乜理由會經濟蕭條二十年噃&hellip;＂二十年＂係點計出嚟嘅呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本樓市跌左30年wow.</blockquote><br />\n日本樓市係跌咗好耐，但唔係話日本經濟蕭條好多年&hellip;＂蕭條＂係有具體條件嘅&hellip;美國上世紀三十年代嘅＂大蕭條＂計到盡都唔夠十年（中間仲有反彈）&hellip;話會有二十年經濟蕭條，係好誇張嘅一種推斷&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你可以話日本經濟不振咗三十幾年，期中有多次經濟衰退，但唔應該話日本經濟蕭條咗三十年&hellip;"},{"pid":"5fefbbcf94acf61ea8e821196ee523b268778480","tid":290454,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a131db98995ab805582f57d0ce733454262f181","tid":290454,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇唔到有乜原因大陸人會賣走港樓.....</blockquote><br />\n賣香港樓，買外國樓</blockquote><br />\n狗都笑<br />\n全球都恐怖襲擊<br />\n唯獨香港最安全<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跌唔係唔得<br />\n香港人暴動，恐怖襲擊，外星人襲港<br />\n咪會囉<br />\n<br />\n跟本唔會跌<br />\n再俾無謂幻想，只會令到愈黎愈多大陸人搶哂樓<br />\n香港人就要返大陸住。<br />\n<br />\n等於港太咁<br />\n跟本無可能，只係一相情願.....<br />\n唉...難接受都要接受架啦"},{"pid":"6ac34c274c64239fafc1aec4beac1fc8ee306256","tid":290454,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇唔到有乜原因大陸人會賣走港樓.....</blockquote><br />